{"tid":1234472,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有英國媒體想寫有關英藉香港警察濫權的報導","createTime":"2019-06-17T02:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T02:09:18.000Z","uid":107302,"like":211,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"651d10b9528103c4eb7c966e4228d22694bed562","tid":1234472,"uid":107302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"《突發》【有英國媒體想寫有關英藉香港警察濫權的報導】請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n現尋求有關英藉香港警察濫權、暴力對抗示威者、不當使用武器的證據，包括相片、影片或受訪者等等。<br />\n<br />\n特別是證據證明英藉香港警察指示使用的武器。<br />\n<br />\n如果有任何幫到手的地方、請inbox聯絡Richard Scotford<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/567628880005099/posts/1860652950702679?s=100001476284569&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F567628880005099%2Fposts%2F1860652950702679%3Fs%3D100001476284569%26sfns%3Dmo&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=11458bc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/567628880005099/posts/1860652950702679?s=100001476284569&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"11026b6cccce75d0f1177bd8cdf79a0bfa8a56ee","tid":1234472,"uid":65710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:27:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94b32fe9a7ab6c349401c6a515ea90990adb8a10","tid":1234472,"uid":107302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:28:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2b840f5f9379627ab73d4f38af9c1c02697aed0e","tid":1234472,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:28:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"466b5929aab265f5a73d469f269f79f0622d379d","tid":1234472,"uid":257598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:28:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JG0TQyWvKV4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJG0TQyWvKV4&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=770ed615\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JG0TQyWvKV4</a>"},{"pid":"dc0a93505128b955c4839b25fa9f5beae0d1df39","